# Garbage Collection

## Read this when

- the repo has drift from many generated changes
- cleanup work keeps slipping behind feature work
- you are reviewing a structural hygiene report

## What to review

- stale docs
- oversized files
- repeated TODO or FIXME hotspots
- suspicious filenames like `v2` or `final-final`
- docs missing from the index

## Cadence

- Replace with a real cadence such as weekly, per release, or daily automation.

## Merge policy

- Prefer reviewable cleanup patches over broad rewrites.
